description:
Comfortable, warm cardigan in a lofty half-cardigan knit that insulates well and is stretchy and easy
to move about in. Made from soft, ethically produced wool with G-1000 Silent Eco reinforcements on
the elbows and pocket openings. Zippered front and a medium-high collar that will keep your neck
warm and cosy. Great all year round for fishing, hunting or outdoor chores around the cabin.
name: Fjallraven Ovik Zip Cardigan Knit - Mens
